  "description": "<i>Sam in Monster's Garden</i> is a freeware collect-'em-up game not completely unlike <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/dig-dug\">Dig Dug</a>. As Sam you have to collect fruits and flowers. As you dig your way to the flowers and fruits you have to watch out for the apples, if they don't have enough supporting ground underneath they will fall down and they can crush you to death.<br><br>Every level is free of monster when it starts but after a while monsters starts to appear. There are two types of monsters: yellow ones and lilac ones. The yellow monsters can only follow existing paths while the lilac ones digs new ones. ",
